headline: ORACLE'S ANNUAL MEETING OF STOCKHOLDERS TO BE HELD NOVEMBER 18, 2025
summary: Oracle (NYSE: ORCL) will hold its 2025 Annual Meeting of Stockholders on Tuesday, November 18, 2025, at 9:00 a.m., Central Time. This year's meeting will be conducted virtually via a live audio webcast at www.virtualshareholdermeeting.com/ORCL2025. Stockholders as of the close of business on September 19, 2025, the record date, are entitled to participate in the Annual Meeting. Guests may also view the Annual Meeting but may not vote or ask questions.
